{"tid":1240673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(炒車)警指揮官612衝突掟磚？　網上片段顯示疑僅舉磚示意","createTime":"2019-06-18T12:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T12:50:13.000Z","uid":264423,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fae07bacc1d8859c5ca009647ec0a3354ec91c05","tid":1240673,"uid":264423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918779/org/06ad7a650387f5dfdc6dc2f984ecbc83.jpg/cAINnm5PMLRdScCIGKsBGRpiP7LMU4PNOx_mfjsf5n4?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918779%2Forg%2F06ad7a650387f5dfdc6dc2f984ecbc83.jpg%2FcAINnm5PMLRdScCIGKsBGRpiP7LMU4PNOx_mfjsf5n4%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=bd97035c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方將6月12日衝突定性為「暴動」，警務處處長盧偉聰解釋當日下午3時多開始，示威者向警察投擲磚頭、鐵枝、木板、鐵馬等，警務人員生命受威脅，形容示威者為「暴徒」。事後有網民圖文並茂反擊，指首先爆發衝擊的立法會示威區（俗稱「煲底」），一名白衣指揮官左手持警棍，右手舉起磚頭，質疑有警員向示威者投擲磚頭。惟從片段可見，該名白衣指揮官疑只是舉磚示意，向在場人士顯示有人向警察掟磚，他其後將磚頭掉在地上。片段亦顯示，指揮官旁一名警員頭部被磚頭扔中。<br />\n<br />\n龍和道對開行人路磚頭被掘起。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918843/org/cd29071d85d26e9983b3dea9b948b740.jpg/zKor7gpVIrJeHWZgh-K5mVZz9NvUxlhJ7kcYCsRHGAo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918843%2Forg%2Fcd29071d85d26e9983b3dea9b948b740.jpg%2FzKor7gpVIrJeHWZgh-K5mVZz9NvUxlhJ7kcYCsRHGAo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=22ddf2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方在6月12日衝突清場行動中使用催淚彈、布袋彈等武器驅散示威者，令人質疑警方使用的武力是否恰當。警隊「一哥」盧偉聰解釋當日警方發現龍和道和夏愨道路面有磚頭被掘起，及至下午三時許大批示威者掟磚等物品，警務人員在生命受威脅的情況下，遂以適當的武力驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n事後網上流傳一名督察舉起磚頭的照片，質疑警方向示威者掟磚。不過有網民上載612遊行紀錄，包括當日在立法會示威區警方與示威者對峙衝突的片段，片中可見該名白衣指揮官疑舉磚示意，徐徐地從後方撿起一塊磚頭，然後舉至頭部高度，稍作揮動，向在場人士顯示有人向警察掟磚，舉起時間達6秒，該片段隨即中斷。片段亦顯示，指揮官旁右手邊一名警員頭部被磚頭扔中，發出「呀」聲。<br />\n<br />\n網上亦有另一條片段，可見該名白衣指揮官疑舉起磚頭後，以警棍指向磚頭，向示威者展示，然後再將磚頭掉在地上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918865/org/7ed21d1a1191ea7f7f392208df6881f7.png/o8i0-NAVmrW4xSo53CCRHioloL_G5IF2g7Pht4Oz4bc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918865%2Forg%2F7ed21d1a1191ea7f7f392208df6881f7.png%2Fo8i0-NAVmrW4xSo53CCRHioloL_G5IF2g7Pht4Oz4bc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6ea0b54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者向警員掟磚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918866/org/a9c4de3b3cff6d30e80eb5d5c8d74dbb.png/tcLVjHPrUNJfJvConRRv4Wp110nZBxYnL8MNYi_DDWI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918866%2Forg%2Fa9c4de3b3cff6d30e80eb5d5c8d74dbb.png%2FtcLVjHPrUNJfJvConRRv4Wp110nZBxYnL8MNYi_DDWI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9ac87add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者向警員掟磚，擊中警員頭部，警員發出「呀」聲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918869/org/2ebc26896828b2f21eb78d9bf37ca1c4.png/R_FmPj-kDbfiTnjUgNUqntZyJzIijhZD7x3ZSO8d2Ug?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918869%2Forg%2F2ebc26896828b2f21eb78d9bf37ca1c4.png%2FR_FmPj-kDbfiTnjUgNUqntZyJzIijhZD7x3ZSO8d2Ug%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d619e6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衣指揮官舉起磚頭，稍作揮動，向在場人士示意指有人掟磚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918868/org/a137feba4673eca4dd5e77f490956348.png/pMVq4mx0gg9cIR5lb6HXjBtWFjJ6soGpK56DWyueg1s?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918868%2Forg%2Fa137feba4673eca4dd5e77f490956348.png%2FpMVq4mx0gg9cIR5lb6HXjBtWFjJ6soGpK56DWyueg1s%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7033abdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衣指揮官舉起磚頭，稍作揮動，向在場人士示意指有人掟磚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918867/org/6d1b21aedb07fc52bc5104d6df8d1462.png/dwO3omCuULNrir_m46ddy2nTurUAveDo6H6vxOh-r8Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918867%2Forg%2F6d1b21aedb07fc52bc5104d6df8d1462.png%2FdwO3omCuULNrir_m46ddy2nTurUAveDo6H6vxOh-r8Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=14e8738e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衣指揮官舉起磚頭向在場人士示意指有人掟磚，為時6秒，及至該畫面完結也沒有擲出磚頭的動作出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rwkd-jBjXsQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRwkd-jBjXsQ&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=868906bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rwkd-jBjXsQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H0gROnuNi6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH0gROnuNi6U&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=4e73d636\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H0gROnuNi6U</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/341141/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98612%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%8E%9F%E7%A3%9A-%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E7%96%91%E5%83%85%E8%88%89%E7%A3%9A%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F341141%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598612%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%258E%259F%25E7%25A3%259A-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2583%2585%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%25A3%259A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2584%258F&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=ab76b833\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/341141/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98612%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%8E%9F%E7%A3%9A-%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E7%96%91%E5%83%85%E8%88%89%E7%A3%9A%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F</a><br />\n<br />\n香港01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c09f4da7b2d9bc3824f614ea806ec8eac20b4b","tid":1240673,"uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rYKGqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rYKGqd.jpg&h=daa9085b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ba31240b14d7bfb79a842109903b671ff521335","tid":1240673,"uid":183113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"73c09f4da7b2d9bc3824f614ea806ec8eac20b4b","tid":1240673,"uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rYKGqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rYKGqd.jpg&h=daa9085b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"道歉都無露出胸部，一啲常識都無！"},{"pid":"1cb9c43ac6f6ec28c4eea339bb0e34b1e9893b30","tid":1240673,"uid":256143,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"係咪差佬叫d鬼開始做野既暗號呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c607a7e800e0435956e45212b7984edc92e70d","tid":1240673,"uid":71253,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<br />\n反正其他狗又掟鐵支又掟磚<br />\n大撚把片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴打比片上黎"},{"pid":"b0e206af8a4ca87ed31299072dc4829f28159b0d","tid":1240673,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:50:13.000Z","msg":"裝睡的人是叫不醒的<br />\n你要選擇性失明我冇辦法"}]}